          { question: "Can we visit the D-Day beaches from this route?", answer: "Yes, your driver can arrange a detour or circuit including Omaha Beach, the American cemetery at Colleville-sur-Mer or Pointe du Hoc. Request a personalised quote when booking." },
          { question: "Is a stop at Avranches possible?", answer: "Yes, a 20-30 minute stop at Avranches is recommended for the Scriptorial (Mont-Saint-Michel manuscripts) and the bay panorama from the Jardin des Plantes." }
